# Loger Logistics MVP - Complete Codebase

## üöÄ Project Overview
**Loger** - SaaS logistics platform for SMBs in Tier 2/3/4 cities in India. "Stripe for SMB Logistics Infrastructure" with Delivery-as-a-Service (DAAS) and wallet-based pricing.

**MVP Features:**
- ‚úÖ Scheduling system with calendar interface
- ‚úÖ Pre-populated delivery templates (‚Çπ100/‚Çπ200/‚Çπ150)
- ‚úÖ OTP-based authentication with session management
- ‚úÖ Wallet management and transactions
- ‚úÖ Real-time order tracking and analytics
- ‚úÖ Production-ready configuration

---

